Business Brief -- Pharmakinetics Laboratories Inc.:
   Coopers Picked to Succeed
   Deloitte as Accounting Firm
The company and Deloitte said it hadn't had any
disagreements with Deloitte involving accounting practices
and procedures.
   The company had filed for protection from creditors in
late 1990; last June, the company and a former official
pleaded guilty to obstructing an investigation in the generic
drug industry, and the company agreed to paid a $200,000
fine.